articles.text:
In a video making the rounds online, a dog is seen displaying its artistic skills on canvas.

The dog which was seen working without any guidance from its owner shocked people on social media.

In the video, the dog is seen showing off the different colors it intends to use for the painting and it used the brush to effortlessly paint a flower as though it were a human.

When the dog was done, it posed with the finished artwork and had a cute puppy smile

Reacting, @StevenLam29; I wonder how much effort did she put in to train this dog? cause damn, this dog is so smart, it might as well be a human! My dog is useless af but I still love her

